### how to encript a file
    # vim file1
    # ansible-vault encript file1
    
### how to view a vault or encripted file
    # ansible-vault view file1

### how to edit a file in encripted mode only
    # ansible-vault edit file1

### how to decript a file
    # ansible-vault decript file1

### how to create file directly on encription mode 
    # ansible-vault create file2
    
### how to run a ansible-playbook in vault or encripted mode 
    # ansible-playbool file1.yml --ask-vault-pass
